  "title": "The Future of Distributed MRV  🔭 📱| Roundup #52",
  "slug": "refi-roundup-52",
  "html": "<p><strong><em>Hi Everybody!  </em></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/afreezyfrench\"><strong><em>Adam French</em></strong></a><strong><em> here to lead the roundup for this week 👋</em></strong><em> I'm a designer of strategies, brands, and business models, currently working with </em><a href=\"https://twitter.com/dMeter4dmrv\"><em>dMeter</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"https://silvi.earth/\"><em>Silvi</em></a><em> in the ReFi space and in the early stages of founding Interform - a transformation agency weaving regenerative values, design thinking, and universal principles together to help organizations and their ecosystems evolve. </em></p><p><em>Here is the roundup for this week👇</em></p><hr><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/refi-roundup-52.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"439\" height=\"439\"><figcaption>An augmented AI image \"Regenerative Finance Roundup\" from <a href=\"midjourney.com\">Midjourney</a></figcaption></figure><h1 id=\"mrv-needs-a-reboot-%F0%9F%91%A8%F0%9F%8F%BB%E2%80%8D%F0%9F%92%BB\">MRV Needs a Reboot 👨🏻‍💻</h1><p>The creation of carbon credits, as well as credits for any positive impact you can imagine (clean water, clean energy, biodiversity, recycling, etc..), have the potential to be a critical piece of the puzzle in providing funding for public goods and creating more regenerative economic systems. Yet to date, early manifestations of these types of market have been riddled with problems - from a lack of transparency and integrity, to the proliferation of cheap and low-quality credits. A recent study conducted by the Guardian suggested more than <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2023/jan/18/revealed-forest-carbon-offsets-biggest-provider-worthless-verra-aoe\">90% of rainforest carbon offsets by biggest certifier are not having their intended impact</a>!</p><p>These issues are slowing the market down and delaying progress in combatting climate change when time is running out. Where do we go from here?</p><h3 id=\"mrv-innovation-%F0%9F%99%8F\">MRV Innovation 🙏 </h3><p>Measurement, Reporting and Verification (MRV) is the process of collecting, monitoring and verifying data on any impact claim that is made. It is an essential part of the process to overcome the aforementioned issues with carbon credits, yet presently, there are a number of challenges for implementing MRV effectively:</p><ul><li>Too expensive or complicated for small landholders to participate.</li><li>Relies on centralized bodies with limited output and are prone to <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2023/jan/18/revealed-forest-carbon-offsets-biggest-provider-worthless-verra-aoe\">reporting errors</a>.</li><li>Current methodologies have limited biodiversity and social impact capabilities, creating a lack of justice &amp; equity for <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/environment/earth-insight/2014/jul/03/world-bank-un-redd-genocide-land-carbon-grab-sengwer-kenya\">indigenous communities</a>.</li></ul><p>As a result, there is a critical need for innovation in MRV processes and solutions with support from an array of people and advanced technologies - AI, satellite imagery, drone surveillance, and of course.. blockchain. </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/Screenshot-2023-02-20-at-3.27.06-pm.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2000\" height=\"525\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/02/Screenshot-2023-02-20-at-3.27.06-pm.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/02/Screenshot-2023-02-20-at-3.27.06-pm.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/02/Screenshot-2023-02-20-at-3.27.06-pm.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w2400/2023/02/Screenshot-2023-02-20-at-3.27.06-pm.png 2400w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption><strong><a href=\"https://rmi.org/what-can-blockchain-do-for-carbon-markets\">Beyond the Buzz: What Can Blockchain Do for Carbon Markets?</a></strong></figcaption></figure><p>Decentralized-ledger technologies such as blockchain have the potential to help increase transparency, reduce transaction costs and combat fraudulent actions such as <a href=\"https://www.compensate.com/articles/what-is-double-counting-and-why-is-it-such-a-big-deal\" rel=\"noopener\">double counting</a>. As such, lets dive into some awesome projects innovating at the intersection of Web3 &amp; decentralized MRV (dMRV) 👇🏽</p><h3 id=\"open-forest-protocol-%E2%80%93-open-and-scalable-dmrv-%F0%9F%8C%B2\">Open Forest Protocol – open and scalable dMRV 🌲</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.openforestprotocol.org/\">Open Forest Protocol</a> (OFP)  allows forest projects of any size to Measure, Report, and Verify their forestation data. Using mobile app solutions to make it easier and more affordable for small landholders to participate in the carbon markets. See the <a href=\"https://openforestprotocol.medium.com/protecting-a-3-500-hectare-ecosystem-in-tanzania-kisampa-conservancy-b41aea62a1f9\">Kisampa Conservancy</a> in Tanzania as a case study here.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><a href=\"https://twitter.com/OpenForest_\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-17.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/02/image-17.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/02/image-17.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-17.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a><figcaption><strong><strong><strong><a href=\"https://openforestprotocol.medium.com/protecting-a-3-500-hectare-ecosystem-in-tanzania-kisampa-conservancy-b41aea62a1f9\">Protecting a 3,500 Hectare Ecosystem in Tanzania: Kisampa Conservancy</a></strong></strong></strong></figcaption></figure><h3 id=\"regen-networkdmrv-and-origination\">Regen Network - dMRV and origination</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.regen.network/\">Regen Network</a> has built the <a href=\"https://app.regen.network/\">Regen Registry</a> with the goal to create open-source infrastructure for cost-effective and rigorous MRV implementation. Their aim is to democratize and invigorate ReFi by empowering communities of earth stewards, scientists, technologists, and climate entrepreneurs to govern the systems used to create new ecological assets. To that end, the registry is built on the understanding that ecological systems are inherently complex and a one-size-fits-all solution is unlikely to meet the unique challenges and opportunities of each ecological regeneration project. </p><p>See the <a href=\"https://library.regen.network/v/regen-registry-program-guide/\">Regen Registry Guide</a> for more info or check out <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/sam-bennetts-a044681a1/\">Sam Bennett</a>'s <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2rT9uqO1YF8&amp;list=PLArKB4hKFyGG5ByacytlCsvUBc1hm_-oU\">deep dive video</a> into their pioneering soil carbon dMRV capabilities... 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-bookmark-card\"><a class=\"kg-bookmark-container\" href=\"https://library.regen.network/v/regen-registry-program-guide/\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-content\"><div class=\"kg-bookmark-title\">Regen Registry Guide - Regen Library</div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-description\"></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-metadata\"><img class=\"kg-bookmark-icon\" src=\"https://app.gitbook.com/public/images/icon-512.png\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"kg-bookmark-author\">Regen Library</span></div></div><div class=\"kg-bookmark-thumbnail\"><img src=\"https://www.gitbook.com/cdn-cgi/image/width&#x3D;256,height&#x3D;40,fit&#x3D;contain,dpr&#x3D;1,format&#x3D;auto/https%3A%2F%2F284303808-files.gitbook.io%2F~%2Ffiles%2Fv0%2Fb%2Fgitbook-x-prod.appspot.com%2Fo%2Fspaces%2FWs38YRExASMl7tOmp6pp%2Flogo%2FmwtW27XPPAE7id5aoLjB%2FFavicon_b.png%3Falt%3Dmedia%26token%3Db27c181a-4baa-4b4f-b2fb-3d61459013f8\" alt=\"\"></div></a></figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/2rT9uqO1YF8?list=PLArKB4hKFyGG5ByacytlCsvUBc1hm_-oU\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen></iframe></figure><h3 id=\"gainforestusing-ai-and-desci-to-measure-and-reward-nature-stewardship-%F0%9F%9B%B0\">GainForest - using AI and DeSci to measure and reward nature stewardship 🛰</h3><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/GainForestNow\">GainForest</a> is a non-profit working to utilise AI monitoring systems, decentralized science (DeSci), and impact NFTs to unlock funding for nature-based solutions. They have recently released an extremely cool demo for their Forest Map, check it out below 🌲 🗺️ 👇 </p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Forget Google Maps. Have you ever dreamed of a <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ForestMap?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#ForestMap</a>? I know we have! Check it out! (yes, it even rotates 360º). How did this happen, though? 🧵 <a href=\"https://t.co/uz9iEbvSNu\">pic.twitter.com/uz9iEbvSNu</a></p>&mdash; GainForest 🛰(🌱) (@GainForestNow) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/GainForestNow/status/1623750463282679809?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 9, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"bicowgblockchain-infra-carbon-offset-working-group-%F0%9F%8F%97%EF%B8%8F\">BICOWG - Blockchain Infra Carbon Offset Working Group 🏗️</h3><p><a href=\"https://bicowg.org/\">BICOWG</a> is a collaborative brain trust that assists in coordinating crypto-climate projects, provides education and spaces/forums for Q&amp;As, develops tooling for emissions-related methodologies, and provides clearinghouse services required for the industry-wide movement to address blockchain’s climate impact.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">GH PART I 🧵...<br><br>A few weeks ago, BICOWG gathered leading operators at the intersection of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Climate?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Climate</a> x <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Crypto?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Crypto</a> space across <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Web2?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Web2</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Web3?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Web3</a> during our inaugural event <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GreenHouseRetreat2022?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#GreenHouseRetreat2022</a>.<br><br>Our focus was on “Interoperability” across Language, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Code?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Code</a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Tokens?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Tokens</a>. 🌳<br><br>1/ <a href=\"https://t.co/T19rAVLJPn\">pic.twitter.com/T19rAVLJPn</a></p>&mdash; BICOWG (@BICOWG) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BICOWG/status/1587131499492610054?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 31, 2022</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h3 id=\"dmeteran-interoperable-platform-for-dmrv-%F0%9F%99%8C%F0%9F%8F%BD\"><strong>dMeter - An Interoperable platform for dMRV </strong>🙌🏽</h3><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/dMeter4dmrv\">dMeter</a> is a DAO experimenting with advanced data collection methods to approach dMRV. Envisioning a future where anyone can get paid for their regenerative action. Building an accessible and interoperable toolkit to help communities get recognized and paid for their actions by connecting existing dMRV projects.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Very interesting convo, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/defi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#defi</a> to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/refi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#refi</a> &amp; <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/desci?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#desci</a> to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/resci?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#resci</a> need <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/dMRV?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#dMRV</a><br><br>Special thanks to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/DmrvNetwork?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@DmrvNetwork</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/orgo?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@orgo</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EverGreenCoin_?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@EverGreenCoin_</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReSciNetwork?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ReSciNetwork</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/regenagbundle?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@regenagbundle</a>!<br><br>Our grant at <a href=\"https://t.co/jvFymUqE1k\">https://t.co/jvFymUqE1k</a>, speakers pls post link to your grants below &amp; we&#39;ll reshare?<a href=\"https://t.co/u6ciirzQnO\">https://t.co/u6ciirzQnO</a></p>&mdash; dMeter (@dMeter4dmrv) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/dMeter4dmrv/status/1615759147882143744?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">January 18, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><h2 id=\"outlook-for-dmrv-this-year-%F0%9F%94%AD\">Outlook for dMRV this year 🔭</h2><p>Major funding has yet to come to dMRV, but demand is higher than ever.. We hope 2023 will be the year we see dMRV scale and proliferate across the world as an integral part of the evolving impact asset and credit markets. As always, we will be keeping our eyes peeled for new projects, solutions and deals 👀🕵 - let us know if we missed any!👇</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://ctt.ac/irWQc\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Share Roundup!</a></div><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/02/ReFi-Cover.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/02/ReFi-Cover.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"%F0%9F%94%A5-projects-of-the-week\">🔥 Projects of the Week</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"ema-showcase-of-top-voted-projects-from-the-refi-dao-websiteem\"><em>A showcase of top voted projects from the ReFi DAO website!</em></h3><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/projects\" class=\"kg-header-card-button\">View More</a></div><p>Here were the top 5 most voted projects of the week at <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-roundup-51/refidao.com\">refidao.com</a>:</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/projects\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-29.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/02/image-29.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/02/image-29.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/02/image-29.png 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-29.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></a></figure><ol><li>🦋 <strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ecosapiensxyz\">Ecosapiens</a></strong>: World’s first perpetual carbon-capture NFT.</li><li>️🌙 <strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/LunCoSim\">LunCo</a></strong>: Opensource Engineering Software for Space.</li><li>🥬 <a href=\"https://www.raiz.farm/\"><strong>Raiz</strong></a>: Vertical farming network with tokenization model. </li><li>🏠 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xUrbanika\"><strong>Urbánika</strong></a>: Facilitating urban commons DAOs and city-wise coordination.</li><li>⚡ <a href=\"https://twitter.com/PowerLedger_io\"><strong>PowerLedger</strong></a>: Building the operating system for the new energy markets</li></ol><p><em>*Projects included in <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-roundup-51/\">roundup #51</a> are not counted this week!</em></p><p><strong><strong>Votes have now been reset</strong></strong> so head over to <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-roundup-51/refidao.com\">refidao.com</a>, make an account, and show some support to your favourite projects in the ecosystem this week! 💚</p><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.refidao.com/projects\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Vote away!</a></div><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-6.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover-6.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-podcasts-%F0%9F%8E%99%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi Podcasts 🎙️</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emtop-audio-and-video-content-from-creators-across-the-web-em%F0%9F%98%8A\"><em>Top audio and video content from creators across the web </em>😊</h3></div><h2 id=\"thallo-on-refi-podcast-%F0%9F%99%8C\">Thallo on ReFi Podcast 🙌</h2><p><a href=\"https://podcast.refidao.com/\">ReFi Podcast</a> Bonus Episode - <strong>Pragmatic Carbon Finance with </strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hayleymoller\"><strong>Hayley</strong></a><strong> &amp; </strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/RyanGled\"><strong>Ryan</strong></a><strong> from Thallo. </strong>This episode dives deep into <a href=\"https://www.thallo.io/\">Thallo's</a> innovation of a two-way carbon credit bridge to bring liquidity and transparency to on and off-chain carbon markets. Read the <a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-deep-dive-impactmarket/\">deep dive</a>, <a href=\"https://podfollow.com/refi-podcast/view\">listen</a> on your podcasting favorite platform, or check out the <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=or-lXoWEJHg\">episode on Youtube</a> 👇</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><iframe width=\"200\" height=\"113\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/or-lXoWEJHg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" allowfullscreen title=\"ReFi Podcast BONUS Episode: Pragmatic Carbon Finance with Hayley &amp; Ryan from Thallo\"></iframe></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://podfollow.com/refi-podcast/view\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Listen to the episode</a></div><h2 id=\"other-%F0%9F%94%A5-podcasts-on-our-radar\">Other 🔥 Podcasts on our Radar:</h2><ul><li><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/episode/3Vcbotp5johyBhlRgQnXvm\"><strong>Impact networks &amp; decentralizing social media</strong></a>  featuring <a href=\"https://twitter.com/breno_navi\">Breno</a> from <a href=\"https://ekonavi.com/\">Ekonavi</a>- Episode #7o of the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Block_Explore\">Block Explorer</a> with <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/cbrightfield/\">Colin Brightfield</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CashUpton\">Cash Upton</a></li><li><a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/episode/4fNevF2LrYTmlhL1oQbEsS?si=edfa2f48fdf04936\"><strong>Solving Extreme Poverty with a Stablecoin</strong></a> feat. <a href=\"https://twitter.com/jasdrie\">Jasper</a> and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/Geyr_Garmr\">Garm</a> of <a href=\"https://twitter.com/glodollar\">Glo Dollar</a> 🏛️ | Greenpill episode #89 with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/owocki\">Kevin Owocki</a></li></ul><hr><div class=\"kg-card kg-header-card kg-width-full kg-size-small kg-style-image\" style=\"background-image: url(https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover.png)\" data-kg-background-image=\"https://blog.refidao.com/content/images/2023/01/ReFi-Cover.png\"><h2 class=\"kg-header-card-header\" id=\"refi-newsbites-%F0%9F%97%9E%EF%B8%8F\">ReFi NewsBites 🗞️</h2><h3 class=\"kg-header-card-subheader\" id=\"emthe-latest-updates-across-refi-twitter-and-beyondem\"><em>The latest updates across ReFi Twitter and beyond...</em></h3></div><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card kg-card-hascaption\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/vardan-papikyan-JzE1dHEaAew-unsplash.jpg\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/02/vardan-papikyan-JzE1dHEaAew-unsplash.jpg 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/02/vardan-papikyan-JzE1dHEaAew-unsplash.jpg 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1600/2023/02/vardan-papikyan-JzE1dHEaAew-unsplash.jpg 1600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/vardan-papikyan-JzE1dHEaAew-unsplash.jpg 1920w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"><figcaption>What it looks like when ReFi Spring and ReFi DAO Merge.&nbsp;</figcaption></figure><h2 id=\"%F0%9F%A4%9C%F0%9F%8F%BC-a-merger-of-refi-community-powerhouses-%F0%9F%A4%9B%F0%9F%8F%BC\">🤜🏼 A Merger of ReFi Community Powerhouses 🤛🏼</h2><p><a href=\"https://www.refispring.com/\">ReFi Spring </a>has officially MERGED with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist\">ReFi DAO</a> to create an epic platform called the Event Organizer Guild for ReFi community. This partnership between <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RefiSpring\">ReFi Spring</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/commonsstack\">Commons Stack</a>, and <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist\">ReFi DAO</a>, is aimed at empowering people &amp; communities to build local ReFi Nodes across the globe...</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">We are super excited to announce that ReFi Spring is merging with <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ReFiDAOist</a>! 🎉<br><br>Together we can build a global startup movement rooted in local communities! 🎉🥂<br><br>To celebrate, we wanted to announce our first seven grantees for S2! 👐<br><br>Read more on <a href=\"https://t.co/IrxMVttWV8\">https://t.co/IrxMVttWV8</a><br><br>1/</p>&mdash; ReFi Spring 🤝 ReFi DAO (@RefiSpring) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RefiSpring/status/1625610999184363520?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 14, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card\"><img src=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-30.png\" class=\"kg-image\" alt loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1600\" height=\"897\" srcset=\"__GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w600/2023/02/image-30.png 600w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/size/w1000/2023/02/image-30.png 1000w, __GHOST_URL__/content/images/2023/02/image-30.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 720px) 720px\"></figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"__GHOST_URL__/refi-spring-has-merged-with-refi-dao/\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Read the Full Post Here</a></div><h2 id=\"%F0%9F%92%B0-refi-bounty-mania-from-future-quest-%F0%9F%92%B0\">💰 ReFi Bounty Mania from Future Quest 💰</h2><p><a href=\"https://future.quest/\">Future Quest</a> has created a bounty board with $50K of bounties for 17 different ReFi projects. There are a variety of tasks, from social media posting to hosting a roundtable around specific topics in ReFi. It's a great opportunity for any bounty hunters or people looking to get into the door working in ReFi.</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Exciting news! Announcing our $50k bounty board to support the development of our 17 cohorts in the recent ReFi grant pool supported by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/0xPolygon?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@0xPolygon</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/CeloOrg?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@CeloOrg</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/bobanetwork?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@bobanetwork</a> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ReFiDAOist?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">@ReFiDAOist</a>. <br><br>Don&#39;t miss out on this opportunity to get involved in the ReFi industry: <a href=\"https://t.co/1ebcbwyQPv\">https://t.co/1ebcbwyQPv</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/2DyrxMekPK\">pic.twitter.com/2DyrxMekPK</a></p>&mdash; Future Quest | Let&#39;s 🤝 in Denver! (@FutureQuestDAO) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/FutureQuestDAO/status/1626364527007653894?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 16, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://app.dework.xyz/future-quest-60153/future-quest-bounty/view/open-tasks-le4apquz\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Find a Bounty Here</a></div><h2 id=\"%F0%9F%8C%B1-ecosapiens-announced-their-inaugural-nft-drop\">🌱 Ecosapiens Announced their Inaugural NFT Drop! </h2><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/ecosapiensxyz\">Ecosapiens</a> has diligently built a strong community in ReFI. It's time for the community to buy NFT collectibles, each one backed by 16 tons of carbon kept out of the atmosphere. Dropping on Feb 22nd!</p><figure class=\"kg-card kg-embed-card\"><blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">One year ago, we raised $1.5M in VC to bring something truly innovative to web3: the world&#39;s first carbon-backed collectibles.<br><br>We are thrilled to announce the launch of our EcoGenesis collection, a limited edition of 350 pieces that go live on Feb 22nd.<br><br>More below (1/17) 🧵👇 <a href=\"https://t.co/13G2blidH7\">pic.twitter.com/13G2blidH7</a></p>&mdash; Ecosapiens (@ecosapiensxyz) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ecosapiensxyz/status/1623774271146442753?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 9, 2023</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n</figure><div class=\"kg-card kg-button-card kg-align-center\"><a href=\"https://www.addevent.com/event/jm16137077\" class=\"kg-btn kg-btn-accent\">Add the Drop to Your Calendar</a></div><h2 id=\"%F0%9F%8F%9D%EF%B8%8F-refi-india-greenpill-festival-hackathon-registration-is-now-open\">🏝️ ReFi India Greenpill festival: hackathon 